<p>Speaking of which, you cannot go to the palace without a proper wardrobe. Grace Kelly combined film star glamour with royalty chic and this is the look to channel at Palazzo Parisio. A cocktail style, black bustier dress is always a good start. My fit and flare dress emphasises the waistline and makes your legs look endless. Because the dress has such a wow factor, keep accessories to a minimum. Tanned skin and perfume was my choice.</p>

