<p>A ball at the palace is true fairy-tale time so make the dress the star. My stunning, blush coloured, fitted dress by <a href="https://ellezeitoune.com.au/new-arrivals" target="_blank">Elle Zeitoune</a> is worthy of a royal wedding with its fishtail train and multiway sash. Emphasise your waist, tie to one wrist or use as a stole, the choice is yours. Again, keep accessories to a minimum and let the dress do the talking.</p>

<p>And, at the end of a perfect evening, the perfect boudoir. Palazzo Parisio, I love you</p>

